name: It's Not My Fault! (V)
Text: 'Use 1 Force to take [Virtual Block 6] Phylo Gandish or an Immediate Effect into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  OR  Use 2 Force to take an Effect that deploys for free into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.  OR  If a Dark Jedi on table, retrieve Return Of The Jedi into hand.',
